# GODO
### Clean and simple go *todo-cli* app.

### Clone the project
```
git clone https://github.com/alojine/godo.git
```

### Build the project
```
cd godo
make build/godo
```
### Run with flags
```
./godo --flag
```

- **--add {Some sample text}**
- **--complete {Index of the task that was completed}**
- **--list**
- **--del {Index of the task to be deleted}**
- **--clear**